{
  "description": "不怕没柴烧。",
  "goal": "(-> (not (box (not A))) (diamond A))",
  "premise": [],
  "guides": [
    {
      "text": "反方向：如果 ¬A 不必然成立，那么 A 可能成立。这里用 `diamond-def-rev`。",
      "tactic": null
    },
    {
      "text": "假设 ¬□¬A。",
      "tactic": "(assume (not (box (not A))))"
    },
    {
      "text": "用 `diamond-def-rev` 将 ¬□¬A 折叠回 ◇A。",
      "tactic": "(diamond-def-rev 1)"
    },
    {
      "text": "消去假设。两个方向一起确立了 ◇A ↔ ¬□¬A。",
      "tactic": "(->-intro (not (box (not A))) 2)"
    }
  ],
  "hints": [],
  "unlocks": [
    {
      "name": "diamond-def-rev",
      "rule": "\\frac{\\Gamma \\vdash \\lnot \\Box \\lnot A}{\\Gamma \\vdash \\Diamond A}",
      "description": "◇-定义反向：将 ¬□¬A 折叠回 ◇A。",
      "syntax": "(diamond-def-rev N)",
      "example": "1. ⊢ ¬□¬A\n2. (diamond-def-rev 1)  →  ⊢ ◇A"
    }
  ]
}